{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673130/extras/Killing_The_Real_Pain.gif?t=1735768519\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Blue Protagonist is being imprisoned and tortured in a small cell by three characters:   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Real Pain, the prison's boss who is red and has mustache. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Biggest Vain, a giant and mysterious knight who prevents prisoners from escaping. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Smallest Stain, a psychopath who enjoys killing others with a shotgun.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But suddenly, the door opens and now the only thing he wants is vengeance.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Help him exit his cell and jump over the obstacles on his way to find and kill everyone who has made him suffer. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Storytelling using gameplay, with a few cutscenes and no dialogue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Minimalist art and music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3 unconventional boss fights.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">5 levels, each set in a different location.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Influenced by the works of Albert Camus, specifically <i>The Stranger</i> and <i>The Myth of Sisyphus.</i></p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673130/page_bg_gen